Rebrand code-server env vars to COMPOSERY_*

Renames every CODE_SERVER_*/CS_* environment variable and the {{CS_STATIC_BASE}}
template token that code-server reads to the COMPOSERY_* namespace, with no
fallback, so the code-server name can never leak into operator configuration.
Covers operator-facing config (CONFIG, HOST, COOKIE_SUFFIX, IDLE_TIMEOUT_SECONDS,
RECONNECTION_GRACE_TIME, DISABLE_FILE_DOWNLOADS, DISABLE_GETTING_STARTED_OVERRIDE,
DISABLE_PROXY) and internal IPC/template tokens (PARENT_PID, SESSION_SOCKET,
STATIC_BASE; both set and read sites move together). The matching overlay HTML
pages use {{COMPOSERY_STATIC_BASE}}.

